<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <head>
        <meta charset="UTF-8">
        <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
        <title>Apeiro | Game</title>
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="./css/main.css">
        <script src="./js/game.js" defer></script>
        <script type="text/javascript" defer>
            window.addEventListener("beforeunload", function (e) {
                var confirmationMessage = "Are you sure you want to leave this page? Any unsaved changes will be lost.";
                e.returnValue = confirmationMessage;
                return confirmationMessage;
            });
        </script>
    </head>

    <body id="game-page">
        <div class="fade in"></div>
        <h1 id="message">Your Journey Begins...</h1>
        <div id="custom-prompt">
            <div id="custom-prompt-box">
                <span>
                    <h2>Enter your custom prompt:</h2>
                    <a id="custom-prompt-close">x</a>
                </span>
                <p>Use the input field to type in a custom scenario, question, or dialogue that you want the AI to respond to. Be as detailed or as vague as you like</p>
                <textarea id="custom-prompt-input" maxlength="100" placeholder="e.g. I make an escape out of the prison."></textarea>
                <a id="custom-prompt-submit">Submit</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="ui">
            <div id="left-panel">
                <div id="health-bar">
                    <img class="heart" draggable="false" src="./css/images/heart.png">
                    <img class="heart" draggable="false" src="./css/images/heart.png">
                    <img class="heart" draggable="false" src="./css/images/heart.png">
                    <img class="heart" draggable="false" src="./css/images/heart.png">
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="center-panel">
                <div id="narration-box">
                    &emsp;You find yourself standing at the edge of a bamboo forest, the air thick with the scent of damp earth and blooming cherry blossoms. Sunlight filters through the emerald canopy, painting dappled patterns on the moss-covered ground. Birdsong fills the air, a melodious symphony unlike anything you've ever heard. Welcome to the heart of an anime-style forest in Japan, where magic and wonder hide behind every towering tree.\n\nYou've been drawn here by a whisper on the wind, a promise of adventure. But which path will you choose?
                </div>
            </div>
            <div id="right-panel">
                <div id="option-boxes">
                    <a class="option-box" id="option1">1. Follow a winding dirt path that disappears into the thick foliage.</a>
                    <a class="option-box" id="option2">2. Head towards a small, moss-covered shrine nestled beneath a giant wisteria tree.</a>
                    <a class="option-box" id="option3">3. Listen for the sound of a rushing stream and follow its course.</a>
                    <a class="option-box" id="option4">4. Climb a nearby tree for a better view of the surrounding landscape.</a>
                </div>
                <img src="./css/images/custom.svg" id="custom-prompt-btn">
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>
